>> Install some Debian packages:

    # apt-get update
    # apt-get install -y build-essential python2.7 bind9 nginx nano

>> Install Node.js (7.x for now):

    # apt-get install python-software-properties
    # curl -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_7.x | sudo -E bash -
    # apt-get install nodejs

>> Install some global NPM packages:

    # npm install -g gulp pm2

>> Install and run Cloud9:

    (See: https://github.com/c9/core/)
    # pm2 start ~/c9sdk/server.js -n c9 -- --auth "hessam:ahs 502" --listen 0.0.0.0 -w ~ --port 8080
    # pm2 save

>> Create a new SSH key and add it to GitHub's account.

>> Clone VPS project from GitHub:

    # git clone git@github.com:ahs502/VPS.git
    # cd VPS
    # npm i

>> Configure BIND9 and Nginx: (Within the 'VPS/' folder)

    # nano config.js   # Configure the settings
    # gulp




